channel.title: Best place for my pure to train strength on f2p?
channel.description:
Hello, this is a picture of my pure:
(Don't click the advertisment tmobile below its illegal) [IMG]http://u.ultb.net/1225329991.bmp[/img]
Where do you think the best place ot train my pure is on f2p, because ive been looking around and I cannot find anywhere!
Once ive got 75 strength and 60 attack, I'm going members.
Thanks, James

item.title: Best place for my pure to train strength on f2p?
item.dc:creator: @bootnecklad bootnecklad
item.description:
@bootnecklad wrote:

Your best bet is (as mentioned) SOS. Good xp and most of it is agro; nice and easy so sit back stick uyourself in the middle of the monsters and listen to some music, then run away and come back to refresh the agro. I do this a lot its great xp.
